General Assembly House Joint
Resolution No. 15
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 1213
Referred to Committee on JUDICIARY
Introduced by:
REP. STAFSTROM, 129th Dist.
SEN. WINFIELD, 10th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE NOMINATION OF THE HONORABLE
MARGARITA HARTLEY MOORE OF MILFORD TO BE A JUDGE OF
THE SUPERIOR COURT.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the nomination by His Excellency, the Governor, of the
2 Honorable Margarita Hartley Moore of Milford to be a Judge of the
3 Superior Court, to serve for a term of eight years from May 3, 2026, is
4 approved and confirmed, and she is appointed a Judge of the Superior
5 Court for said term.
LCO No. 1213 1 of 1

